title: 773: BITCOIN TESTS TRADERS’ NERVES AS TOP CRYPTO ANALYST REISSUES $450K BTC PRICE FORECAST!!
description:
Popular Crypto analyst Michaël van de Poppe updated us with his latest peak high bull cycle predictions for Bitcoin, Ethereum, Polkadot, Chainlink, Cardano, Zilliqa, Elond and DIA.

The analyst forecasts Bitcoin surging parabolic to $350K-$450K with Ethereum hitting $10,000-$17,500 while noting that some of these predictions 'might be conservative'.
